...New AVIATION, MARINE...

.SYNOPSIS...
Issued at 101 AM PDT Tue Mar 12 2024

Light rain showers this morning will give way to a prolonged dry
period across the region as high pressure builds across the
eastern Pacific. Breezy to gusty northerly winds will develop on
Wednesday into Thursday. High pressure remains nearby into the
weekend with mild temperatures and dry conditions expected.

